# Stripe local dev guidance:
# - STRIPE_SECRET_KEY typically starts with "sk_test_" in test mode.
# - STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET starts with "whsec_". For local dev, get it from Stripe CLI:
#     stripe listen --events checkout.session.completed,customer.subscription.updated,customer.subscription.deleted \
#       --forward-to http://localhost:3000/api/stripe/webhooks
#   Then copy the displayed signing secret to STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET.
# - Payment Links should look like https://buy.stripe.com/... (test mode is fine).
#   Configure each link's success URL to http://localhost:3000/confirmation (or /dashboard)
#   and cancel URL to http://localhost:3000/ .
# - Ensure the Stripe Product used by these links has metadata: membership=pro